{
  "comment": "Self-arming native-compiler ratchet. native_files lists corpus models (rel paths) the native path compiles bit-identically vs the XML oracle; native_count is the floor. NC1/NC1b: compiler/option/size/statistic/visual blocks, default classes, the body tree, primitive geoms, all joint types, frames, sites/cameras/lights, mocap, keyframes, contact pairs/excludes. NC2 adds the drive/constraint families: equality (connect/weld body|site + joint/tendon polycoef, eq_data packing lifted from the XML reader OneEquality), tendons (spatial site/geom/pulley wraps + fixed joint paths, wrap arrays, nJten), actuators (motor/position/velocity/intvelocity/damper/cylinder/adhesion with joint/jointinparent/tendon/body transmission; mjs_setTo* lowering lifted; na/actadr, nJmom, inheritrange, tri-state limits), and sensors (site/joint/tendon/actuator/body/frame + energy/clock; datatype/needstage/dim tables lifted). NC3 assets add materials (mat_* arrays: rgba/emission/specular/shininess/reflectance/metallic/roughness/texrepeat/texuniform + per-role mat_texid; class-chain+IDL defaults via Effective<Material>; geom/site/tendon matid resolved by name) and builtin procedural textures (gradient/checker/flat + edge/cross/random marks, 2D and cube; Builtin2D/BuiltinCube lifted; tex_* arrays + flat tex_data blob; colorspace recorded), and user-data (inline elevation) height fields (hfield_* arrays; row-flip + [0,1] normalization lifted from mjCHField::Compile + the reader's row reversal; hfield geoms bind size/aabb/rbound via assets-before-body compile), plus the <asset> container. NC3 meshes add user-vertex and OBJ/STL/MSH file meshes (mesh_* arrays: vert/normal/texcoord/face/facenormal/facetexcoord, convex-hull graph via qhull, coplanar-face polygons + polygon map, principal-axis inertia frame + boxsz, per-face circumcenters + AABB feeding the shared face BVH appended after body BVH nodes; the parse+process pipeline is lifted from user_mesh.cc + the obj/stl decoder plugins). A mesh geom binds size/aabb/rbound from the mesh aamm, accumulates the mesh frame, and takes inertia from the mesh volume/box; file meshes resolve via mju_openResource (meshdir+strippath) and carry a mesh_pathadr into m->paths. Also fixed a keyframe partial-array bug (ExpandKeyframe pads a short qpos/qvel/act/ctrl/mpos/mquat keeping the authored prefix; the tail defaults) exposed by the newly-admitted asset models. Still fall back: file/cube-face textures (texture.file, until PNG loading lands), hfield-file/skin assets, plugin/SDF meshes, mesh-fit geoms (a primitive type referencing a mesh), <size memory|nstack|njmax|nconmax>, geom fluidshape, replicate/attach, flex/flexcomp/composite, plugins; and the documented NC2 descopes -- muscle/dcmotor/plugin actuators, actuator site/refsite/slidercrank transmission and delay buffers, cylinder bias (upstream stack-UB), tendon material/armature, plugin/user/tactile/contact/rangefinder/camprojection/insidesite/geom-distance sensors, cross-spelling actuator class defaults, partial-array size class defaults (eager-copy tail), per-body sleep and joint springdamper (AutoSpringDamper).",
